## Scope

This MIT License applies to the **source code** of the Pen & Paper project only.

The following are NOT covered by this license and are reserved under separate terms — see `CONTENT-LICENSE`:

- Editorial writing (specimens, field notes, colophon copy, microcopy).
- Photography and image assets (pen and paper photography, ink-on-paper samples, figure plates).
- Design assets specific to the author (logo, wordmark, typographic branding).
- The `.impeccable.md` design context document.

Third-party assets under this repository (fonts, code libraries, etc.) are governed by their own licenses as indicated in `package.json` and the respective source files.
